TY  - JOUR
T1  - Female Labor Supply, Human Capital, and Welfare Reform
AU  - Blundell, Richard
AU  - Costa Dias, Monica
AU  - Meghir, Costas
AU  - Shaw, Jonathan
Y1  - 2016/09/01
